Installation
------------
Dependencies:

ruby >= 1.8 
rails = 1.2.2
  if you use a different rails version, edit config/environment.rb: RAILS_GEM_VERSION
sqlite3-ruby bindings

Note that your browser needs to have javascript enabled to use remo.



WEBrick installation
--------------------
- Get remo from http://remo.netnea.com
- tar xvf remo-x.x.x.tar.gz
- cd remo-x.x.x
- ruby script/server
- direct browser to http://localhost:3000/main/index


Mongrel installation
--------------------
Note that mongrel is not part of the remo distribution.
You can get it from http://mongrel.rubyforge.org

- Get remo from http://remo.netnea.com
- tar xvf remo-x.x.x.tar.gz
- cd remo-x.x.x
- mongrel_rails start -d -e production -a 127.0.0.1 -p 3000
- direct browser to http://localhost:3000/main/index   

